props.content: Creating a neobank or interested in being an account affiilliate? Want to develop a fine cial app that accesses bank account translations? Leverage our Accounts API and your customers will be able to create a new checking account within minutes and access key account data through your site or app data through tour site or app. Get to know your customer better gain critical insights into your customers and use their transaction history and real time info to serve them better. Checking their balances in real time can help with account budgeting.
